  "code": "sequenceDiagram\n    Client->>+LoadBalancer: HTTPS GET /\n    LoadBalancer->>+NGINX: HTTP(Education_ClassroomService) GET /\n    loop route\n        NGINX ->> NGINX: Route based on Host/ServerAlias\n    end\n    NGINX->>+Webservice: HTTP GET /\n    Webservice->>-NGINX: HTTP 302/200 (Education_GradeSync)\n    NGINX->>-LoadBalancer: HTTP 302/200 (Education_StudentDB)\n    LoadBalancer->>-Client: HTTP 302/200 (Education_LMS_Portal)",
