  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个教育系统的请求流转图。场景是用户访问我们的LMS门户，流量先经过负载均衡，然后由NGINX做路由分发，最终落到具体的教学服务上。我想体现四个核心业务：课堂服务、成绩同步、学生数据库和LMS门户本身。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Client",
        "LoadBalancer",
        "NGINX",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我梳理一下：Client用HTTPS打到LoadBalancer，LoadBalancer再转HTTP到NGINX，NGINX内部有个路由决策环，然后转发到Webservice，最后响应按原路返回，但每层返回时标注对应的业务模块？比如Webservice返回时带GradeSync，NGINX返回时带StudentDB？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Client",
        "LoadBalancer",
        "NGINX",
        "Webservice",
        "loop route"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，就是这个逻辑。NGINX那个路由环要画出来，它是根据Host和ServerAlias做内部转发的。还有注意箭头方向——前三个请求是实线箭头带加号，表示同步调用；返回用虚线箭头，也是带加号的实线箭头样式。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NGINX",
        "loop route",
        "Host/ServerAlias"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画第一版：Client到LoadBalancer是HTTPS GET，LoadBalancer到NGINX标注HTTP(Education_ClassroomService)，然后NGINX内部画route循环，再到Webservice。返回链上Webservice回NGINX标GradeSync，NGINX回LoadBalancer标StudentDB，最后LoadBalancer回Client标LMS_Portal。状态码用302/200。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Client",
        "LoadBalancer",
        "NGINX",
        "Webservice",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "HTTP 302/200"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，LoadBalancer到NGINX的那一步，Education_ClassroomService的标注位置不对。应该是NGINX到Webservice才带ClassroomService，LoadBalancer到NGINX只是普通的HTTP转发，不绑定具体业务。还有NGINX内部循环的标注应该是\"route\"，不是\"routing\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "LoadBalancer",
        "NGINX",
        "Webservice",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "loop route"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "收到，修正：LoadBalancer到NGINX改为纯HTTP GET /，NGINX到Webservice才带上HTTP(Education_ClassroomService)。循环标注改回\"route\"。同时确认所有返回虚线都带加号，状态码302/200保留。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "LoadBalancer",
        "NGINX",
        "Webservice",
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "loop route",
        "HTTP 302/200"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "现在对了。再确认一下返回链的数据流：Webservice返回GradeSync，NGINX返回StudentDB，LoadBalancer返回LMS_Portal——这个顺序体现了每层网关向上层屏蔽下层细节的设计。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Webservice",
        "NGINX",
        "LoadBalancer",
        "Education_GradeSync",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_LMS_Portal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认完毕。完整链路：Client-HTTPS→LoadBalancer-HTTP→NGINX-[route循环]→Webservice，返回时逐级携带业务标识，最终Client拿到LMS_Portal响应。结构清晰，可以定稿。",
